ime anywhere using their smartphones tablets or computers in addition working with its remote sensors the ecobee recognizes which rooms are occupied and automatically adjusts the temperature based on the readings in those rooms if a user’s schedule changes and he or she leaves the home the sensors will recognize this and prevent the heating and cooling systems from running unnecessarily when a home is empty the more sensors included the smarter the ecobee becomes at delivering comfort where it matters and savings where it counts the ecobee doesn’t use power stealing which can result in sudden and unexpected failure particularly during extreme hot or cold weather the ecobee rather has a consistent power source that is hardwired in — meaning a user can trust the ecobee will continue to deliver comfort regardless of the weather ecobee inc  infoecobeecom wwwecobeecom eproduct  want more hvac industry news and information join the news on facebook twitter and linkedin today did you enjoy this article click here to subscribe to the news magazine test related articles ecobee thermostats go on the road honeywell intl inc residential wifi thermostat wifi thermostats transcend the market ecobee announces integration with amazon echo related products understanding txv refrigeration systems superheat and subcooling dvd installing residential forced air furnaces hvac customer service handbook th edition evaluating refrigeration systems troubleshooting  identifying problems continued related events whole building control from concept to reality the abcs of unico pcbs failure avoidance  system technologiesac inld fast related directories ecobee inc rcs technology inc bp porter inc heat pump controlsthermostats lightstat inc you must login or register in order to post a comment report abusive comment thank you for helping us to improve our forums is this comment offensive please tell us why subscription center more videos sponsored content sponsored content is a special paid sectio