ment is detected the ecobee integrates the remote sensors by controlling to the average room temperature for all sensors that are included in the mode setting and detect occupancy if enabled a vacation mode can be programmed for extended times away from home with this smart thermostat you can set convenient reminders for hvac maintenance furnace filter replacement uv lamp replacement as well as alerts for low temperature high temperature low humidity and high humidity model smart smart si ecobee st generation ecobee nd generation ecobee lite ecobee model number ebstat ebsmartsi ebecobee ebstate ebstatel announcement date october   january   september   june   october   may   launch price  usd  usd  usd  usd dimensions  x  x  inches  x  x  inches  x  x  inches  x  x  inches  x  x  inches  x  x inches room sensors wired requires remote sensor module added to equipment interface module wireless max  historyedit ecobee was founded in  it has been recognized with a number of awards including the deloitte technology green  award for canadian green technology companies and the  ahr expo innovation award in the category of building automation integrationedit ecobee products integrate with amazon alexa apple homekit samsung smartthings wink haiku fans ifttt logitech harmony vera and control ecobee uses an open api for additional integration options referencesedit  ecobee crunchbase   dow georgia june   using the ecobee wifi thermostat with your apple watch imore   wollerton megan september   ecobee wifi smart thermostat review cnet   wollerton megan september   ecobee wifi smart thermostat review cnet   ecobee smart wifi thermostat pc mag january     ifttt integration comes to ecobee ecobee   introducing the ecobee channel ifttt blog   clover juli june   ecobee and insteon announce new homekitcompatible products macrumors   kahn jordan june   here comes apple’s homekit first products start shipping starting w insteon lutron ihome elgato and ecobee to mac   cooper sean  octob